## Sona Code Interface

```sona
intent: "detect developer emotional state from runtime pattern"

# Detection
emotion.detect(
  sources: [SOURCE_RUNTIME, SOURCE_STRUCTURE],
  backend: "default"
)

# Resulting state (auto-populated by detection engine)
emotion.state = {
  type: FRUSTRATED,
  intensity: 4,
  source: SOURCE_COMPOSITE,
  confidence: 0.85,
  detected_at: time.now(),
  context: "12 consecutive TypeErrors in 4 minutes",
  contributing_sources: [
    { source: SOURCE_RUNTIME,    intensity: 4, confidence: 0.91 },
    { source: SOURCE_STRUCTURE,  intensity: 3, confidence: 0.78 }
  ]
}

# Response (deterministic — state × intensity → strategy)
emotion.respond(
  state: emotion.state,
  strategy: "simplify_output"
)

# Receipt logging (automatic when audit: true)
emotion.log(audit: true)
```

