## Receipt Integration

Every emotional detection event is a first-class receipt entry. The receipt contains:

```json
{
  "event_type": "emotion_detection",
  "state": "FRUSTRATED",
  "intensity": 4,
  "source": "SOURCE_COMPOSITE",
  "confidence": 0.85,
  "strategy_fired": "simplify_output",
  "backend": "default",
  "context": "12 consecutive TypeErrors in 4 minutes",
  "contributing_sources": [
    { "source": "SOURCE_RUNTIME",    "intensity": 4, "confidence": 0.91 },
    { "source": "SOURCE_STRUCTURE",  "intensity": 3, "confidence": 0.78 }
  ],
  "detected_at": "2025-04-18T10:23:44Z",
  "policy_applied": "prod",
  "receipt_hash": "<sha256>"
}
```

This receipt entry is signed, tamper-evident, and replayable under the Sona 0.11.0 receipt system. The composite calculation can be verified independently from the stored contributing source scores.

